-- Ankle Injury Rules Out QPR’s Wright-Phillips for Rest of Season
-- B y   D a n i e l l e   R o s s i n g h
-- 2013-04-05T08:49:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-05/ankle-injury-rules-out-qpr-s-wright-phillips-for-rest-of-season.html
Queens Park Rangers player Shaun
Wright-Phillips won’t be in action for the rest of the season
because of an ankle injury, the London club said.  The midfielder had surgery earlier this week on his right
ankle and has now been ruled out for the remainder of the
Premier League season, QPR said in a statement on its website
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Danielle Rossingh in London at 
